{
  "name": "TextEffectFormat",
  "summary": "<p>使用 <strong>TextEffect</strong> 属性可返回一个 <strong>TextEffectFormat</strong> 对象。</p>\n<p><b class=\"mainheaders\">示例</b></p><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*下例为第一张工作表上的形状一设置字体名称及格式。要运行本示例，形状一必须是艺术字对象。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> worksheet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">TextEffect</span> = worksheet.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Shapes</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextEffect</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">TextEffect</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">FontName</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Courier New&quot;</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">TextEffect</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">FontBold</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">TextEffect</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">FontItalic</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例显示活动工作表的第三个艺术字的字号。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shape = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(shape.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextEffect</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">FontSize</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
  "description": "<p>包含应用于艺术字对象的属性和方法。</p>\n",
  "category": "et",
  "properties": [
    {
      "name": "Alignment",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置一个 <strong>MsoTextEffectAlignment</strong> 值，它代表艺术字的对齐方式。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例向第一张工作表中添加艺术字对象，然后将该对象设置右对齐。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shapes = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shape = shapes.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">AddTextEffect</span>(msoTextEffect1, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Test Text&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Palatino&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">54</span>, <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>, <span class=\"hljs-literal\">false</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">50</span>)\n    shape.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextEffect</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Alignment</span> = msoTextEffectAlignmentRight\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例显示活动工作表的第一个艺术字的对齐方式是否为居中对齐。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shape = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(shape.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextEffect</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Alignment</span> == msoTextEffectAlignmentCentered)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "MsoTextEffectAlignment",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "Application",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>如果不使用对象识别符，则该属性返回一个 <strong>Application</strong> 对象，该对象表示 ET 应用程序。如果使用对象识别符，则该属性返回一个表示指定对象（可对一个 OLE 自动操作对象使用本属性来返回该对象的应用程序）创建者的 <strong>Application</strong> 对象。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<p>本示例显示一条有关创建 myObject的应用程序的消息。  </p>\n<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> myObject = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveWorkbook</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (myObject.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value</span> == <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;ET&quot;</span>) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;This is an ET Application object.&quot;</span>)\n    } <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span> {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;This is not an ET Application object.&quot;</span>)\n    }\n}\n</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "Object",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Creator",
      "summary": "<p>如果该对象是在 ET 中创建的，则此属性返回字符串 XCEL，它等同于十六进制的数字 5843454C。<strong>Creator</strong> 属性是为 Macintosh 上的 ET 设计的，在 Macintosh 上，每个应用程序都具有一个四字符的创建者代码。例如，ET 的创建者代码为 XCEL。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 32 位整数，该整数指示在其中创建此对象的应用程序。只读 <strong>Long</strong> 类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "",
      "type": "number（int4 精度）",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "FontBold",
      "summary": "<div id=\"vstable\" style=\"font-family:&quot;white-space:normal;\"><table><thead><tr>\n<th><strong>MsoTriState</strong> 可以是下列 <strong>MsoTriState</strong> 常量之一。</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody><tr>\n<td><strong>msoCTrue</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoFalse</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTriStateMixed</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTriStateToggle</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTrue</strong> 指定的艺术字为粗体。</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>",
      "description": "<p>如果指定艺术字中的字体格式为加粗，则该属性值为 <strong>msoTrue</strong>。<strong>MsoTriState</strong> 类型，可读写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*如果第一张工作表上的第三个形状为艺术字，本示例将该形状的字体加粗。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> worksheet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shape = worksheet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (shape.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Type</span> == msoTextEffect) {\n        shape.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextEffect</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">FontBold</span> = msoTrue\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例显示活动工作表的第二个艺术字的字体是否加粗。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shape = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(shape.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextEffect</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">FontBold</span> == msoTrue)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "MsoTriState",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "FontItalic",
      "summary": "<div id=\"vstable\" style=\"font-family:&quot;white-space:normal;\"><table><thead><tr>\n<th><strong>MsoTriState</strong> 可以是下列 <strong>MsoTriState</strong> 常量之一。</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody><tr>\n<td><strong>msoCTrue</strong> 不应用于该属性。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoFalse</strong> 指定的艺术字对象中的文字不是倾斜的。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTriStateMixed</strong> 不应用于该属性。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTriStateToggle</strong> 不应用于该属性。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTrue</strong> 指定的艺术字对象中的文字是倾斜的。</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>",
      "description": "<p>如果指定艺术字中的字体是倾斜的，则返回 <strong>msoTrue</strong>。<strong>MsoTriState</strong> 类型，可读写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将第一张工作表中第四个形状的字体设置为斜体。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> worksheet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    worksheet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">4</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextEffect</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">FontItalic</span> = msoTrue\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例显示活动工作表的第二个艺术字是否为斜体。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shape = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(shape.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextEffect</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">FontItalic</span> == msoTrue)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "MsoTriState",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "FontName",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置指定艺术字的字体名称。<strong>String</strong> 类型，可读写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将第一张工作表上第三个形状的字体名称设置为 Courier New（如果形状为艺术字）。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> worksheet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shape = worksheet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (shape.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Type</span> == msoTextEffect) {\n        shape.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextEffect</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">FontName</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Courier New&quot;</span>\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例显示活动工作表的第二个艺术字的字体名称。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shape = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(shape.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextEffect</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">FontName</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "string",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "FontSize",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>以磅为单位返回或设置指定艺术字的字体大小。<strong>Single</strong> 类型，可读写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将第一张工作表中第四个艺术字的字号设置为 16 磅。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> worksheet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    worksheet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">4</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextEffect</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">FontSize</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">16</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例显示活动工作表的第二个艺术字的字号。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shape = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(shape.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextEffect</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">FontSize</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（float 精度）",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "KernedPairs",
      "summary": "<div id=\"vstable\" style=\"font-family:&quot;white-space:normal;\"><table><thead><tr>\n<th><strong>MsoTriState</strong>可以是下列 <strong>MsoTriState</strong> 常量之一。</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody><tr>\n<td><strong>msoCTrue</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoFalse</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTriStateMixed</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTriStateToggle</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTrue</strong>指定艺术字中的字符对自动紧缩。</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>",
      "description": "<p>如果指定艺术字中的字符对是自动缩紧的，则该属性值为 <strong>msoTrue</strong>。<strong>MsoTriState</strong> 类型，可读写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例打开第一张工作表中第三个形状（如果该形状为艺术字）的字符对自动紧缩。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> worksheet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shape = worksheet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (shape.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Type</span> == msoTextEffect) {\n        shape.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextEffect</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">KernedPairs</span> = msoTrue\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例显示活动工作表的第二个艺术字的字符对是否打开自动紧缩。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shape = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(shape.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextEffect</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">KernedPairs</span> == msoTrue)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "MsoTriState",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "NormalizedHeight",
      "summary": "<div id=\"vstable\" style=\"font-family:&quot;white-space:normal;\"><table><thead><tr>\n<th><strong>MsoTriState</strong>可以是下列 <strong>MsoTriState</strong> 常量之一。</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody><tr>\n<td><strong>msoCTrue</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoFalse</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTriStateMixed</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTriStateToggle</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTrue</strong>指定艺术字中的所有字符（无论大小写）均为同一高度。</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>",
      "description": "<p>如果指定艺术字中所有字符（无论大小写）均为同一高度，则该属性值为 <strong>msoTrue</strong>。<strong>MsoTriState</strong> 类型，可读写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将包含文本“Test Effect”的艺术字添加到第一张工作表，并为新的艺术字命名为 texteff1。然后，该代码使名为 texteff1 的形状中的所有字符的高度相同。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> worksheet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    worksheet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">AddTextEffect</span>(msoTextEffect1, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Test Effect&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Courier New&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">44</span>, <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>, <span class=\"hljs-literal\">false</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">10</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">10</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Name</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;texteff1&quot;</span>\n    worksheet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;texteff1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextEffect</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">NormalizedHeight</span> = msoTrue\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例显示活动工作表的第二个艺术字的所有字符是否为同一高度。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shape = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(shape.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextEffect</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">NormalizedHeight</span> == msoTrue)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "MsoTriState",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "Parent",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回指定对象的父对象。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "",
      "type": "Object",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "PresetShape",
      "summary": "<div id=\"vstable\" style=\"font-family:&quot;white-space:normal;\"><table><thead><tr>\n<th><strong>MsoPresetTextEffectShape</strong>可以是下列 <strong>MsoPresetTextEffectShape</strong> 常量之一。</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody><tr>\n<td><strong>msoTextEffectShapeArchDownCurve</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTextEffectShapeArchDownPour</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTextEffectShapeArchUpCurve</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTextEffectShapeArchUpPour</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTextEffectShapeButtonCurve</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTextEffectShapeButtonPour</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTextEffectShapeCanDown</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTextEffectShapeCanUp</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTextEffectShapeCascadeDown</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTextEffectShapeCascadeUp</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTextEffectShapeChevronDown</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTextEffectShapeChevronUp</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTextEffectShapeCircleCurve</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTextEffectShapeCirclePour</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTextEffectShapeCurveDown</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTextEffectShapeCurveUp</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTextEffectShapeDeflate</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTextEffectShapeDeflateBottom</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTextEffectShapeDeflateInflateDeflate</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTextEffectShapeDoubleWave1</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTextEffectShapeFadeDown</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTextEffectShapeFadeRight</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTextEffectShapeInflate</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTextEffectShapeInflateTop</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTextEffectShapePlainText</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTextEffectShapeRingOutside</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTextEffectShapeSlantUp</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTextEffectShapeTriangleDown</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTextEffectShapeWave1</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTextEffectShapeDeflateInflate</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTextEffectShapeDeflateTop</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTextEffectShapeDoubleWave2</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTextEffectShapeFadeLeft</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTextEffectShapeFadeUp</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTextEffectShapeInflateBottom</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTextEffectShapeMixed</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTextEffectShapeRingInside</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTextEffectShapeSlantDown</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTextEffectShapeStop</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTextEffectShapeTriangleUp</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTextEffectShapeWave2</strong></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div><p>设置 <strong>PresetTextEffect</strong> 属性会自动设置 <strong>PresetShape</strong> 属性。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置指定艺术字的形状样式。<strong>MsoPresetTextEffectShape</strong> 类型，可读写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将第一张工作表上所有艺术字的形状设置为中心点向下的 V 形。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> worksheet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> s = <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>; s &lt;= worksheet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>; s++) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (worksheet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(s).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Type</span> == msoTextEffect) {\n            worksheet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(s).<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextEffect</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PresetShape</span> = msoTextEffectShapeChevronDown\n        }\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例显示活动工作表的第二个艺术字的形状是否成功设置成msoTextEffectShapeChevronUp。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shape = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    shape.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextEffect</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PresetShape</span> = msoTextEffectShapeChevronUp\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(shape.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextEffect</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PresetShape</span> == msoTextEffectShapeChevronUp)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "MsoPresetTextEffectShape",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "PresetTextEffect",
      "summary": "<p>该属性的值与**“艺术字库”**对话框内的格式（按从左至右和从上至下的顺序编号）相对应。</p>\n<div id=\"vstable\" style=\"font-family:&quot;white-space:normal;\"><table><thead><tr>\n<th><strong>MsoPresetTextEffect</strong> 可以是下列 <strong>MsoPresetTextEffect</strong> 常量之一。</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody><tr>\n<td><strong>msoTextEffect1</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTextEffect10</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTextEffect11</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTextEffect12</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTextEffect13</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTextEffect14</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTextEffect15</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTextEffect16</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTextEffect17</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTextEffect18</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTextEffect19</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTextEffect2</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTextEffect20</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTextEffect21</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTextEffect22</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTextEffect23</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTextEffect24</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTextEffect25</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTextEffect26</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTextEffect27</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTextEffect28</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTextEffect29</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTextEffect3</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTextEffect30</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTextEffect4</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTextEffect5</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTextEffect6</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTextEffect7</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTextEffect8</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTextEffect9</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTextEffectMixed</strong></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div><p>设置 <strong>PresetTextEffect</strong>属性会自动设置指定形状的许多其他格式属性。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置指定艺术字的样式。<strong>MsoPresetTextEffect</strong> 类型，可读写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将第一张工作表上所有艺术字的样式设置为艺术字库对话框中列出的第一个样式。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> worksheet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> s = <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>; s &lt;= worksheet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>; s++) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (worksheet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(s).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Type</span> == msoTextEffect) {\n            worksheet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(s).<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextEffect</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PresetTextEffect</span> = msoTextEffect1\n        }\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例显示活动工作表的第三个艺术字的形状是否为艺术字库对话框中列出的第二个样式。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shape = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(shape.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextEffect</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PresetTextEffect</span> == msoTextEffect2)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "MsoPresetTextEffect",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "RotatedChars",
      "summary": "<div id=\"vstable\" style=\"font-family:&quot;white-space:normal;\"><table><thead><tr>\n<th><strong>MsoTriState</strong> 可以是下列 <strong>MsoTriState</strong> 常量之一。</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody><tr>\n<td><strong>msoCTrue</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoFalse</strong>指定艺术字中的字符保留原有的相对于边框形状的方向。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTriStateMixed</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTriStateToggle</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTrue</strong>将指定艺术字中的字符相对于艺术字边框形状旋转 90 度。</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div><p>如果艺术字中含有水平文字，将 <strong>RotatedChars</strong>属性设置为 <strong>msoTrue</strong> 可将该字符逆时针旋转 90 度。如果艺术字中含有垂直文字，将 <strong>RotatedChars</strong> 属性设置为 <strong>msoFalse</strong> 可将该字符顺时针旋转 90 度。使用 <strong>ToggleVerticalText</strong> 方法在水平文字流和垂直文字流之间切换。</p>\n<p><strong>Shape</strong> 对象的 <strong>Flip</strong> 方法和 <strong>Rotation</strong> 属性以及 <strong>TextEffectFormat</strong> 对象的 <strong>RotatedChars</strong> 属性和 <strong>ToggleVerticalText</strong> 方法会对表示艺术字的 <strong>Shape</strong>对象中的字符的方向和文字排列的方向产生影响。可能必须经过试验才能找到组合使用这些属性和方法的最佳途径以达到预期效果。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>如果指定艺术字对象中的字符相对于该对象旋转了 90 度，则该值为 <strong>msoTrue</strong>。如果指定艺术字对象中的字符相对于该对象保持原有方向，则该值为 <strong>msoFalse</strong>。<strong>MsoTriState</strong> 类型，可读/写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将包含文本“Test”的艺术字添加到第一张工作表，并将字符逆时针旋转 90 度。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> worksheet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> newWordArt = worksheet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">AddTextEffect</span>(msoTextEffect1, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Test&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Arial Black&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">36</span>, <span class=\"hljs-literal\">false</span>, <span class=\"hljs-literal\">false</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">10</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">10</span>)\n    newWordArt.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextEffect</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">RotatedChars</span> = msoTrue\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例显示活动工作表的第二个艺术字的字符是否相对于艺术字的边框形状旋转 90 度。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shape = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(shape.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextEffect</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">RotatedChars</span> == msoTrue)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "MsoTriState",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "Text",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置指定对象中的文本。<strong>String</strong> 型，可读写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将第一张工作表中第三个艺术字的文本设置成“示例文本”。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shape = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>)\n    shape.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextEffect</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Text</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;示例文本&quot;</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例显示活动工作表的第四个艺术字的文本。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shape = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">4</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(shape.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextEffect</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Text</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "string",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "Tracking",
      "summary": "<p>以下表格相对于用户界面上的可用设置给出 <strong>Tracking</strong>属性的值。</p>\n<div id=\"vstable\" style=\"font-family:&quot;white-space:normal;\"><table><thead><tr>\n<th>用户界面设置</th>\n<th>相应的 Tracking 属性值</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody><tr>\n<td>很紧</td>\n<td>0.8</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>紧密</td>\n<td>0.9</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>正常</td>\n<td>1.0</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>稀疏</td>\n<td>1.2</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>很松</td>\n<td>1.5</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置指定艺术字中每个字符的水平间隔相对于字符宽度的比例。该比例可为从 0 到 5 之间的值。（为该属性指定的值越大，字符间的空间越大；小于 1 的值会产生字符重叠）。可读写。<strong>Single</strong> 类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将包含文本 Test 的艺术字添加到第一张工作表，并指定字符间距非常紧密。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> worksheet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> newWordArt = worksheet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">AddTextEffect</span>(msoTextEffect1, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Test&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Arial Black&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">36</span>, <span class=\"hljs-literal\">false</span>, <span class=\"hljs-literal\">false</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>)\n    newWordArt.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextEffect</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Tracking</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">0.8</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例显示活动工作表的第一个艺术字中每个字符的水平间距相对于字符宽度的比例。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shape = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(shape.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextEffect</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Tracking</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（float 精度）",
      "readonly": false
    }
  ],
  "functions": [
    {
      "name": "ToggleVerticalText",
      "summary": "<p>使用 <strong>ToggleVerticalText</strong> 方法可以交换代表艺术字的 <strong>Shape</strong> 对象的 <strong>Width</strong> 和 <strong>Height</strong> 属性的值，但不改变 <strong>Left</strong> 和 <strong>Top</strong> 属性。</p>\n<p><strong>Shape</strong> 对象的 <strong>Flip</strong> 方法和 <strong>Rotation</strong> 属性以及 <strong>TextEffectFormat</strong> 对象的 <strong>RotatedChars</strong> 属性和 <strong>ToggleVerticalText</strong> 方法都会影响代表艺术字的 <strong>Shape</strong> 对象中字符方向和文本排列方式。可能必须经过试验才能找到组合使用这些属性和方法的最佳途径以达到预期效果。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>将指定艺术字中的文字排列方向从水平切换为垂直，反之亦然。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将包含文本 Test 的艺术字添加到第一张工作表，并从水平文本流 (指定艺术字样式 的默认值 msoTextEffect1) 切换到垂直文本流。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> worksheet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> newWordArt = worksheet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">AddTextEffect</span>(msoTextEffect1, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Test&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Arial Black&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">36</span>, <span class=\"hljs-literal\">false</span>, <span class=\"hljs-literal\">false</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>)\n    newWordArt.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextEffect</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ToggleVerticalText</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例将活动工作表的第四个艺术字中的文字排列从水平切换为垂直。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shape = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">4</span>)\n    shape.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextEffect</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ToggleVerticalText</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "parameters": [],
      "returns": "void"
    }
  ]
}